    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the CFD hemolysis prediction model has been reviewed and accepted. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; all assessed factors met or exceeded their required credibility levels at MRL 2. The six remaining factors were not assessed in accordance with the MRL 2 scoping determination. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the defined COU.",
